    "language": "en",
    "text": "The invention relates to an artificial lifting system comprising a progressive cavity motor for hydrocarbon&#39;s extraction. In the invention&#39;s system a pump injects a fluid stored in the surface to the progressive cavity motor, located in the basement; the rotation that occurs by the passage of fluid is transmitted to a progressive cavity pump such that the hydrocarbon is pushed toward the surface.",
